<p>The unrenovated Birchcliff bungalows typically have kitchens with standard 30-inch refrigerator alcoves housing Kenmore, Whirlpool, GE, or Frigidaire models that may be 10 to 20 years old. These machines are reliable but develop age-related issues: compressor start relay failure, evaporator fan motor burnout, thermostat inconsistency, and door gasket deterioration. Parts for these mainstream brands are readily available, and repairs are straightforward — $120 to $280 for most common issues.</p>
